headline: West Side Tractor Sales Co. Named Newest Trimble Technology Outlet, Serving Customers in Illinois, Indiana and Michigan
summary: Trimble® today announced West Side Tractor Sales Co. as the newest Trimble Technology Outlet. West Side Tractor will now sell Trimble grade control, site positioning systems and correction services technology directly to customers using John Deere earthmoving equipment, including dozers, excavators, motor graders, mini-excavators and compact track loaders.
